sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant UI as Misi Form View
    participant Ctrl as AdminMissionController
    participant Mission as Mission Model
    participant Step as MissionStep Model

    Admin->>UI: Buka form /admin/missions/create
    Admin->>UI: Input Judul, Deskripsi & Pilih Tipe 'Syntax'
    UI->>Ctrl: POST /admin/missions/create
    
    Ctrl->>Mission: create(mission_type='syntax', dll)
    Mission-->>Ctrl: Return $newMission (ID)
    
    Ctrl-->>UI: Redirect to Edit Steps View
    
    Admin->>UI: Input "Key Answer Cell" (Misal: C4) & "Key Answer" (Misal: =SUM(A1:B1))
    UI->>Ctrl: POST /admin/missions/{id}/steps
    
    note over Ctrl,Step: Tidak memerlukan koordinat visual (x/y)
    
    Ctrl->>Step: create(mission_id, key_answer_cell, key_answer)
    Step-->>Ctrl: Success
    
    Ctrl-->>UI: Redirect Back (Success Message)
    UI-->>Admin: Tampilkan langkah misi yang berhasil ditambahkan